import { IonApp, IonButton, IonCol, IonInput, IonItem, IonLabel, IonRouterOutlet, IonRow } from "@ionic/react";
import { Redirect, Route, Switch } from "react-router";

import Contact from '../pages/Contact'
import Otp from '../pages/Otp'
var Error = "to be implemented"
function MainControl() {
    return <IonApp>
        {/* <IonRouterOutlet>
            <Route exact path="/contact" >
                <Contact />
            </Route>

            <Route path="/otp">
                <Otp />
            </Route>
            <Route exact path="/">
                <Redirect to="/contact" />
            </Route>
        </IonRouterOutlet> */}


        <Switch>
            <Route path="/" exact>
                <Redirect to="/contact" />
            </Route>
            <Route path="/contact" component={Contact} />
            <Route path="/otp" component={Otp} />
            <Route path="/otp" component={Otp} />
            <Route component={Error} />
        </Switch>

    </IonApp>

}

export default MainControl;
